        5 May 1994. </li>
    <li>Hazlett, Thomas W., &quot;<i>Looking Backwards.</i>&quot;
        <a href="http://www.reason.org"><b>Reason</b></a>, May
        1993, 70-82. </li>
    <li>&quot;<i>Honor Roll.</i>&quot; <a
        href="http://www.mcs.net/~lpi/"><b>Illinois Libertarian</b></a>,
        April 1993, 10. </li>
